PN,35201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,FCumbria has one of the highest rates
OL,7,Fof skin cancer in the UK, health
OL,8,Fexperts are warning.
OL,10,FDespite the county rarely experiencing
OL,11,Fextremely high temperatures,
OL,12,Fspecialists at North Cumbria
OL,13,FIntegrated Care NHS Foundation Trust
OL,14,Fhave issued a reminder that there is
OL,15,Fno safe limit to sun exposure.
OL,17,FAn elderly population and the
OL,18,Fchangeable weather in Cumbria is said
OL,19,Fto contribute to the high rates.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,FJamie Tiffen, Advanced Clinical
OL,7,FPractitioner for Dermatology, said:
OL,8,F"We have a huge rural population in
OL,9,FCumbria of farmers and people who work
OL,10,Foutside. And even those who don't work
OL,11,Foutside, we like to be outside. The
OL,12,Fweekend comes and we're off walking
OL,13,Fthe fells, around lakes or pottering
OL,14,Fin the garden.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,F"It's easy to go out in the morning
OL,7,Fand think 'it's not going to be that
OL,8,Fwarm, I won't bother with any suncream
OL,9,Ftoday' and then you're half way around
OL,10,Fthe lake or you're at the beach with
OL,11,Fthe kids and then the sun comes out -
OL,12,Fand that's when people get caught out."
OL,14,FRon Gordon has been treated for skin
OL,15,Fcancer twenty times, including skin
OL,16,Fgrafts to his face and head.
OL,18,FHe said: "I think the damage I've had
OL,19,Fmight have been caused by school
OL,20,Fholidays, running around the back lane
OL,21,Fwith just shorts on and no protection.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,F"I've started using sun protection, I
OL,7,Fnever ever go out without a hat, I
OL,8,Fhate wearing hats but I never go out
OL,9,Fwithout a hat - even on a dull day!"
OL,11,FMelanoma is the most serious type of
OL,12,Fskin cancer. The risk increases with
OL,13,Fage but it is the third most common
OL,14,Ftype of cancer for people aged 15 to
OL,15,F35.
OL,17,FSunbed use also increases the risk by
OL,18,F75% in under 35s.
OL,20,FCharlotte Birkett was diagnosed with
OL,21,Fmelanoma when she was in her 20's.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,FShe said: "I've always had pale skin
OL,7,Fso before I'd go on holiday, I'd
OL,8,Fusually go on a sunbed just to get
OL,9,Fthat base tan so I don't burn, or I
OL,10,Fwould get prickly heat and the sunbed
OL,11,Fwould help that.
OL,13,F"Now, I obviously wish I'd never had a
OL,14,Fsunbed at all."
OL,16,FMelanie Leeder, Skin Cancer Specialist
OL,17,FNurse said: "A lot of people think
OL,18,Fusing sunbeds is safe, but what they
OL,19,Fdon't realise is sunbeds expose you to
OL,20,Fhigh levels of UV, often higher than
OL,21,Fthe midday sun.
OL,26,@yD@MOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,F"This radiation damages the skin cells
OL,7,Fover time, which can lead to skin
OL,8,Fcancer, including the most dangerous
OL,9,Ftype, known as melanoma. In the UK,
OL,10,Fthousands of skin cancer cases are
OL,11,Fdirectly linked to sunbed use, which
OL,12,Fmakes it the most preventable cause.
OL,14,FShe added: "Using a sunbed under the
OL,15,Fage of 35 increases your chance of
OL,16,Fmelanoma by 75%, so there is no such
OL,17,Fthing as a safe sunbed or safe 'base
OL,18,Ftan'."
OL,26,@vD@LOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,FDr Adil Sheraz, a British Skin
OL,7,FFoundation spokesperson, said: "It is
OL,8,Fvital we protect ourselves from UV
OL,9,Fradiation and the most important thing
OL,10,Fwe can do is apply suncream and avoid
OL,11,Fthe sun especially around midday.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,F"Sun exposure is the factor that
OL,7,Fcauses skin cancer. It's an
OL,8,Faccumulative process, it's not a
OL,9,Fmatter of being in the sun for one
OL,10,Fday. It's often many years of being in
OL,11,Fthe sun, or even small amounts of sun
OL,12,Fover a prolonged period of time that
OL,13,Fwill eventually cause DNA damage and
OL,14,Fcause our cells to mutate and turn
OL,15,Finto skin cancers.
OL,17,F"They may just look like a little
OL,18,Fblack dot on your skin - but if they
OL,19,Fare changing and their size and colour
OL,20,Fis changing it is something that needs
OL,21,Flooking into."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,FWhen should I seek advice?
OL,8,FA - Asymmetry - If you draw a line
OL,9,Fdown your mole and it looks different
OL,10,Fon both sides
OL,12,FB - Borders - If it is irregular then
OL,13,Fget someone to look at it
OL,15,FC - Colour - If there are different
OL,16,Fcolours in the mole such as blues,
OL,17,Fblacks or greys
OL,19,FD - Diameter - A mole that is larger
OL,20,Fthan 6mm should be checked
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,FE - Evolution - If a mole is changing
OL,7,Fover time get it looked at
OL,9,FDr Sheraz says that people should
OL,10,Fthink about wearing suncream and
OL,11,Fprotection daily, even when
OL,12,Ftemperatures are not surprisingly hot.
OL,14,FHe said: "The UV index today is around
OL,15,F8. The next few days it will remain at
OL,16,F7 and then drop to 6.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779879767
OL,3,CNHS issues warning over high skin
OL,4,Ccancer rates in Cumbria
OL,6,F"We should start putting sun
OL,7,Fprotection on when it is UV factor of
OL,8,F3. So it's not just the last few days,
OL,9,Fwe should of been doing this for the
OL,10,Flast few weeks in fact."
OL,12,FAdvice and support:
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/11
